514
00:38:19,010 --> 00:38:20,270
How come you're here?

515
00:38:20,270 --> 00:38:24,610
My Lady, General wasn't at ease that you came back alone so he immediately sent me over.

516
00:38:24,610 --> 00:38:27,380
He also told me to bring a lot of your daily necessities.

517
00:38:27,380 --> 00:38:30,210
Does he really not plan to let me go back?

518
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:37,800
