Lord Yongning, I hope you can be tolerant.

536
00:39:38,500 --> 00:39:40,000
Consort Mother, you're too courteous.

537
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:42,720
Jin'er is kind at heart. She is occasionally stubborn,

538
00:39:42,720 --> 00:39:46,290
